LessCSS Changelog
=================

v0.1.4
-------------
Sep 29, 2012.

- Fixed compiling only 1 file.
- Fixed original directory removal bug when `output_dir` is set.
- Create directories recursively when `output_dir` is set if they don't exist.


v0.1.3
-------------
Apr, 26 2012.

- Add option to specify compression type.

v0.1.2
-------------

Feb, 22 2012.

- Added `output_dir` option.


v0.1.1
-------------

Feb, 09 2012.

- Added `compiled` option.


v0.1
-----------

Feb, 08 2012.

- First public release.
